---

<section id="about" class="py-24 md:py-56 bg-white overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 max-w-7xl">
    {/* Intro Section */}
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 md:gap-24 mb-48 items-start">
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-16">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-px bg-brand-gold"></div>
            <span
              class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.5em] font-bold text-brand-gold"
              >About Mommente</span
            >
          </div>
          <h2
            class="text-5xl md:text-[6vw] font-sans font-black uppercase tracking-tighter leading-[0.9]"
          >
            The things we use should <span
              class="italic font-serif font-light lowercase text-brand-gold"
              >feel</span
            > considered.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-10">
          <p
            class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-charcoal/90 font-light leading-relaxed max-w-2xl"
          >
            Mommente was created from a simple idea: everyday objects should be
            well-designed and worth the space they take in our lives.
          </p>
          <p
            class="text-lg text-brand-charcoal/70 font-light leading-relaxed max-w-xl"
          >
            We are a collective of modern e-commerce brands, each built with
            intention to turn ordinary essentials into meaningful lifestyle
            pieces. Everything we build is guided by one question: <span
              class="text-brand-charcoal font-medium"
              >"Does this add value to someone's life?"</span
            >
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 pt-12 border-t border-brand-charcoal/5"
        >
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h4
              class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-black text-brand-charcoal"
            >
              The Model
            </h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-brand-charcoal/60 leading-relaxed">
              We operate as a brand ecosystem, ensuring every product meets our
              standard of quality without unnecessary markup.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h4
              class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-black text-brand-charcoal"
            >
              The Result
            </h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-brand-charcoal/60 leading-relaxed">
              Brands that blend thoughtful functionality with a premium
              experience that feels right to own.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-5 relative lg:sticky lg:top-32">
        <div class="aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden bg-brand-gray shadow-2xl">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519085360753-af0119f7cbe7?q=80&w=687&auto=format&fit=crop"
            alt="Ron, Founder"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale brightness-105 hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-1000"
          />
        </div>
        <div
          class="absolute -bottom-10 -left-10 bg-brand-charcoal p-12 text-brand-offwhite hidden xl:block min-w-[300px]"
        >
          <p
            class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.5em] font-black mb-4 text-brand-gold"
          >
            The Founder
          </p>
          <p class="text-4xl font-serif italic mb-6 leading-none">Ron</p>
          <div class="w-12 h-px bg-white/20 mb-6"></div>
          <p
            class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-bold opacity-40 leading-relaxed"
          >
            Strategic Brand Vision &<br />E-Commerce Operations
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Philosophy Highlights */}
    <div
      class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-16 lg:gap-24 pt-32 border-t border-brand-charcoal/5"
    >
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <h3
          class="text-3xl font-sans font-black uppercase tracking-tighter leading-tight"
        >
          Why We Exist
        </h3>
        <p class="text-brand-charcoal/70 text-lg font-light leading-relaxed">
          Too many products feel generic â€” made to sell, not to serve. Mommente
          was founded to challenge that by merging design with utility.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-10">
        <h4
          class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] font-black text-brand-gold"
        >
          Core Focus
        </h4>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          {
            [
              "Thoughtful functionality",
              "Clean, modern design",
              "Accessible quality",
              "Premium experience",
            ].map((item) => (
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-6 group">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-gold group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform" />
                <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-bold text-brand-charcoal/60 group-hover:text-brand-charcoal transition-colors">
                  {item}
                </span>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative p-12 bg-brand-gray/30 rounded-sm">
        <p
          class="text-xl font-serif italic leading-relaxed text-brand-charcoal/80"
        >
          "Instead of chasing trends, we focus on building brands that feel
          timeless, useful, and emotionally connected to the people who use
          them."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
